{"tid":252858,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"東方 A2 - 高鐵管道  石崗車廠權屬內地  消防或須「跨境」救援","createTime":"2017-05-22T01:57:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-22T06:53:59.000Z","uid":77905,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e6c5e8ecae6eea9d188197af8a4ef0379d2b5932","tid":252858,"uid":77905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T01:57:23.000Z","msg":"位處石崗的緊急救援處「屬權」，消息人士透露會與高鐵管道「屬權」一同處理，該處是露天地方，但四周會適當圍封，假如「屬權」歸內地所有，事故發生後乘客由管道疏散至該處等候救援時，可能入境處職員為其辦理本港入境手續。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，消息人士指，假如高鐵管道及緊急救援處「屬權」歸香港所有，雖然會令社會較「心安」，但警員在列車上執行香港法例會遇上難題，因為乘客已辦理出境本港手續或尚未辦理入境本港手續，「到底警察仲拉唔拉得佢？拉咗後香港法律又告唔告得入？」&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170522/mobile/bkn-20170522001046090-0522_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170522%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20170522001046090-0522_00822_001.html&d=q6lxkNJLkMCZuErjOs479DM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=7235ac9a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170522/mobile/bkn-20170522001046090-0522_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"b8a448d20fbfc4f9298aa45aa4dfe29a046eecc9","tid":252858,"uid":4964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T02:01:12.000Z","msg":"晨早估到啦，都連接埋軍營"},{"pid":"ccbc4c8e78bb8f3ecb08090fb551e4661ff533db","tid":252858,"uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T02:03:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>晨早估到啦，都連接埋軍營</blockquote><br />\n高鐵根本係軍事設施"},{"pid":"9f000923f2baeea2b889ac8cb6125ea7d5597eb1","tid":252858,"uid":8009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T02:03:37.000Z","msg":"幾時有追撞事故<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9eb1fea9da03552db2bd0a5d86896648996120e9","tid":252858,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T06:00:53.000Z","msg":"新城寨<img src=\"/assets/faces/